{"tid":1069302,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新手上路即遇險　的士逆線衝　嚇窒學神10秒","createTime":"2019-03-20T01:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T15:03:21.000Z","uid":225464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1543464fdea0b0e7fe68ce97762c2885c29f69","tid":1069302,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>新手上路即遇險 的士逆線衝 嚇窒學神10秒</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FjS8E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FjS8E3&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9DcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5d190044\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FjS8E3</a><br />\n（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Shorten link同網賺link都唔識分嘅on9仔自己去google吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190320/photo/bkn-20190320081511112-0320_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190320081823\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190320%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190320081511112-0320_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190320081823&h=2777bd28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會嚇怕咗學神？<br />\n<br />\n學車新手上路最怕乜？近日何文田有的士逆線行駛，險撞掛上學牌的輕型貨車，學神疑被嚇窒，情況驚險！<br />\n<br />\n片段被上傳至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，周日（17日）上午近11時半，有掛上學牌的客貨車沿巴富街行駛至何文田官立中學對開，欲右轉入石鼓街，突然有的士逆線直衝而至，學神被嚇得立即煞車。<br />\n<br />\n惟的士我行我素，減速後即左轉竄去。學神原地停留逾10秒才重新出發，繼續轉彎行駛。<br />\n<br />\n於鄰線等候的目擊者頓時大呼︰「佢逆線呀？&hellip;&hellip;黐線㗎」、「都話啲人癲㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n網民見狀紛紛怒斥︰「呢啲X街1823佢啦」、「好彩唔係考試，否則實畀佢累死」、「學神都好過佢」、「呢個位都夠膽逆線出，完全睇唔通，的士真係有無牌㗎」。"},{"pid":"b3f22baa598971d79935b926b038bda33f053feb","tid":1069302,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"dc狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d8145249764237de2531e28ebe6ef7d5b47df0","tid":1069302,"uid":19725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:12:24.000Z","msg":"一野慢速撞過去 等收錢系列"},{"pid":"15e29213bbd829e13b495a92838cccdecefbedf6","tid":1069302,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"想請問下 如果我係考緊試，係咁既情況下急brake<br />\n會唔會當我fail ?"},{"pid":"3e4649a4d6b11bb26c6648c671ae44e6c891cd9c","tid":1069302,"uid":97855,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"15e29213bbd829e13b495a92838cccdecefbedf6","tid":1069302,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"想請問下 如果我係考緊試，係咁既情況下急brake<br />\n會唔會當我fail ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:55.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"e5253b51781370872b713bbc9392f40097c5f66e","tid":1069302,"uid":9230,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"15e29213bbd829e13b495a92838cccdecefbedf6","tid":1069302,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"想請問下 如果我係考緊試，係咁既情況下急brake<br />\n會唔會當我fail ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"本來就係要急剎，仲要快過考官踩添，唔通撞埋去會合格？"},{"pid":"eb7cd99d369be8dc3f58ff74dc312db2814fdde0","tid":1069302,"uid":9707,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"15e29213bbd829e13b495a92838cccdecefbedf6","tid":1069302,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"想請問下 如果我係考緊試，係咁既情況下急brake<br />\n會唔會當我fail ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"好睇個官架喎，會話你冇留意路面狀況，一考試考生就係原罪"},{"pid":"a5c94b9d77d145ab48a4885dad5e837229db9ef9","tid":1069302,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"停車咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fffbd63efba898c44ea2e2647ee0715eefe445","tid":1069302,"uid":89801,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"15e29213bbd829e13b495a92838cccdecefbedf6","tid":1069302,"uid":98567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"想請問下 如果我係考緊試，係咁既情況下急brake<br />\n會唔會當我fail ?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20